Cell["\<\
so for the first I-Cat, if M = 2 and C = 1, then U = 2, meaning we will \
unpack twice, BUT since it\[CloseCurlyQuote]s odd i will add one more unpack.
for the second I-Cat, if M = 2 and C = 4, then U = 1/2 = 0.5 = 1 (round up), \
meaning we will unpack once.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.981134796811199*^9, 3.981134920865734*^9}, {
  3.981135243431527*^9, 
  3.9811352698685102`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"1ab8301d-a2dc-4305-bb4e-\
af8a878d6a17"],

