Cell[TextData[{
 "same multiplier, just changing the first I-Cat to even and the second I-Cat \
to odd\nI-Cat 1: U = 2/1 = 2 - unpack twice\nI-Cat 2: U = 2/4 = 0.5 \
\[TildeTilde] 1+1 = 2  - unpack twice \n",
 StyleBox["new note:",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 " after working through it, the second I-Cat only needed to be unpacked once \
so I\[CloseCurlyQuote]m not sure if the odd rule applies for every odd I-Cat. \
Maybe just the first one?"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.981151953574114*^9, 3.981152039949864*^9}, {
  3.9811524941990128`*^9, 3.9811525265863533`*^9}, {3.981152657393572*^9, 
